&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You are a team player:&lt;/strong&gt; At Samsara, sales is a team sport. We help each other out by sharing best practices and focusing on winning as a team. Collaboration is a requirement, not a “nice to have”.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In this role, you will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
